msgid "Looks like the large gate we saw earlier..."
msgstr "看起来像我们之前看到过的大门..."

msgid "Doors?"
msgstr "这是门吗？"

msgid "This is probably an elevator."
msgstr "这可能是个电梯。"

msgid "Lights."
msgstr "灯光。"

msgid "Water?"
msgstr "水？"

msgid "An empty slot where a fuse may fit."
msgstr "一个可以安装保险丝的空槽。"

msgid "(Looks like I have to rearrange the fuses to match the display.)"
msgstr "（看起来我要重新排列这些保险丝，以匹配图标。）"

msgid "An empty fuse slot."
msgstr "一个空的保险丝槽位。"

msgid "Place a fuse?"
msgstr "要放置保险丝吗？"

msgid "Place fuse no.5"
msgstr "放置保险丝5号"

msgid "Place fuse no.10"
msgstr "放置保险丝10号"

msgid "Place fuse no.15"
msgstr "放置保险丝15号"

msgid "Place fuse no.20"
msgstr "放置保险丝20号"

msgid "Place fuse no.25"
msgstr "放置保险丝25号"

msgid "Place fuse no.40"
msgstr "放置保险丝40号"

msgid "Do not"
msgstr "不放"

msgid "It's a spider!"
msgstr "是只蜘蛛！"

msgid "I see that."
msgstr "我看到了。"

msgid "Are you scared of spiders?"
msgstr "你怕蜘蛛吗？"

msgid "Not really."
msgstr "不怕吧。"

msgid "So, what, if you see a spider in your house you just LEAVE it there?!"
msgstr "那，如果你在家里看到一只蜘蛛，你就把它留在那里不管吗？！"

msgid "That's crazy."
msgstr "太吓人了。"

msgid "What else should I be doing?"
msgstr "那我还能做什么？"

msgid "I don't know, most people kill it with a shoe or something."
msgstr "我不知道，大多数人会用鞋之类的东西把它拍死。"

msgid "Why?"
msgstr "为什么呢？"

msgid "I dunno, they crawl and stuff. They're creepy."
msgstr "我不知道，它们会爬来爬去。那可真吓人。"

msgid "Why should it die for something that isn't its fault?"
msgstr "这又不是它的错，为什么要让它死呢？"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "That's fair."
msgstr "有道理。"

msgid "Just so you know, I don't kill spiders."
msgstr "你知道的，我不会杀蜘蛛了。"

msgid "I see."
msgstr "好的。"

msgid "I used to, but now I just put them outside."
msgstr "以前我会这么干，但是现在我会把它们赶到外面去。"

msgid "Great."
msgstr "太棒了。"

msgid "A spider hangs from here."
msgstr "一只蜘蛛悬挂在此处。"

msgid "A spider sits here."
msgstr "一只蜘蛛坐在这里。"

msgid "Take out the fuse?"
msgstr "要取出保险丝吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B1F_ControlRoom.pnc_fusebox_takefuse.choice.Take out the fuse?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Facility_B1F_ControlRoom.pnc_fusebox_takefuse.choice.Take out the fuse?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"
